{\pntext\f2 14.\tab}\f3\lang1055 Uygulamay\f2\u305? projenizde dikkate almak i\f0\lang1033\'e7in, \line settings.py'de a\f2\'baa\u287?\u305?daki gibi INSTALLED_APPS listesinde \line proje ad\u305?n\u305?z\u305? belirtmeniz gerekir:\line\line INSTALLED_APPS = [\line    'django.contrib.admin',\line     'django.contrib.auth',\line     'django.contrib.contenttypes',\line     'django.contrib.sessions',\line     'django.contrib.messages',\line     'django.contrib.staticfiles',\line\line     # myapps\line     '\f3\lang1055 appad\f2\u305?\f0\lang1033 '\f3\lang1055  \tab\f2\lang1033 ]\par
