{\pntext\f2 18.\tab}\cf2\b app i\f0\lang1033\'e7\f3\lang1055 indeki urls i\f0\lang1033\'e7\f3\lang1055 ine \cf0\b0 :\line from django.urls import path\line from. import views\line\line urlpatterns=[path("", views.home)]\par
{\pntext\f2 19.\tab}app i\f0\lang1033\'e7\f3\lang1055 inde \cf2\b templates\cf0\b0  klas\f0\lang1033\'f6\f3\lang1055 r\f0\lang1033\'fc\f3\lang1055  olu\f2\'ba\f3 tural\f2\u305?\f3 m. isim opsiyonel de\f2\u287?\f3 il. i\f0\lang1033\'e7\f3\lang1055 erisinde \cf2\b index.html \cf0\b0 olu\f2\'ba\f3 tural\f2\u305?\f3 m. i\f0\lang1033\'e7\f3\lang1055 erisine  <h1>Hello World</h1> yazal\f2\u305?\f3 m.\par
